<section id="fs-idp118142224" class="critical-thinking">
<title>Critical Thinking Questions</title>
<exercise id="fs-idp17776544">
<problem id="fs-idp98370560">
<para id="fs-idp8810176">Are differences in geography behind the differences in absolute advantages?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp98278288">
<problem id="fs-idp52516016">
<para id="fs-idp155918528">Why does the United States not have an absolute advantage in coffee?</para>
