<para id="fs-idp51412896">Look at <link target-id="fs-idp176454304"/>. Compute the opportunity costs of producing sweaters and wine in both France and Tunisia. Who has the lowest opportunity cost of producing sweaters and who has the lowest opportunity cost of producing wine? Explain what it means to have a lower opportunity cost.</para></problem>
